### NFUA Finance Manager

A web-based finance management application designed for association and member contribution tracking.

Key Features:
- Member management
- Contribution tracking
- Transaction history
- Automatic receipt generation
- Financial summaries
- Configurable application settings

Tech Stack:
- TypeScript
- HTML
- Supabase (Database)
- Netlify (Deployment)

Role:
- Planned system workflow
- Designed application structure
- Implemented features using AI-assisted development
- Tested and deployed the application
